id: D1812
type: Detection
summary: Scan source code for vulnerable 3rd party libraries
description: |
  Scan source code for vulnerable open source and third-party libraries. Software composition analysis (SCA) is the task of identifying open source or third party software in a project that are out of date or have known, existing vulnerabilities.  Not using these vulnerable libraries increases the robustness and security of your applications.  
  
references:
  - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Software_composition_analysis
  - https://owasp.org/www-community/Component_Analysis

metadata:
  - version: 0.1
  - state: draft
